quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  89,1,"By the dawn."
  89,2,"By the ten nights."
  89,3,"By the even and the odd."
  89,4,"By the night as it passes—"
  89,5,"is there in that a sworn oath for whoever has a mind1?"
  89,6,"Have yousg not seen what your Lord did to ʻĀd1—"
  89,7,"Iram,(the city) of the pillars"
  89,8,"whose like has never been created in the lands;"
  89,9,"and Thamûd1, who carved the rocks in the valley;"
  89,10,"and Pharaoh of the stakes?"